Titolo: Inmost

Anno: 2019

Descrizione: Inmost is an platform game developed by Hidden Layer Games and published by Chucklefish. It was released for iOS on October 11, 2019, and later ported to macOS, Microsoft Windows, Nintendo Switch, on August 21, 2020. The game follows the fantasy world of a young girl, an evil stoic knight, and a man in search of answers. These stories are interconnected to a creature which feeds on pain, and is set in two different worlds.